{"tid":2263816,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭委任李小加　做港大校委","createTime":"2020-10-30T07:16:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T07:28:28.000Z","uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6518e8af01979f62bf8c22f1f727af2d987c2577","tid":2263816,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:16:39.000Z","msg":"近日再次爆發副校任命風波的香港大學再有人事變動，政府今天刊憲，身兼港大校監的特首林鄭月娥引用《香港大學條例》，委任明年退任港交所行政總裁的李小加，出任港大校務委員，任命下月 1 日起生效，任期三年。<br />\n<br />\n李小加是港交所行政總裁，亦是全國政協委員，他今年年底將退任港交所行政總裁。<br />\n<br />\n港大校委會是香港大學的管治機關，有管理大學財務、人力資源以及規劃大學未來發展路向的權力，大學的人事任命要經校委會通過，校委會早前就通過任命兩名有清華大學背景的大陸學者宮鵬和申作軍，出任港大副校長。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E6%9D%8E%E5%B0%8F%E5%8A%A0-%E5%81%9A%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%A0%A1%E5%A7%94/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E5%25A7%2594%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%258A%25A0-%25E5%2581%259A%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%25A7%2594%2F&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KKarsW1wokO1n9cqNe5yO8o%3D&h=fdded8c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E5%25A7%2594%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%258A%25A0-%25E5%2581%259A%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%25A7%2594%2F&h=2fc32fe4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E6%9D%8E%E5%B0%8F%E5%8A%A0-%E5%81%9A%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%A0%A1%E5%A7%94/</a>"},{"pid":"a5460f9b54d9af76dc7d6ce7b584925ffe17c39c","tid":2263816,"uid":99962,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:19:13.000Z","msg":"勁共勁共勁共..... Kong U........ 勁共勁共勁共...."},{"pid":"86a56cd1a0c75b048d0596156fb5f1625711015e","tid":2263816,"uid":317874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:21:56.000Z","msg":"XGU+1"},{"pid":"c4a